Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:05.08,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sonoko brought Makoto along to her family house, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.64,0:00:10.02,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sonoko's mother, Tomoko, hates him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.74,0:00:15.04,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And when he sees Sonoko's excitement at the mention of Kaitō Kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.16,0:00:17.52,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}"Kid{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-sama{\r\be10}"?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.16,0:00:19.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.44,0:00:21.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-Advisor!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.14,0:00:26.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name is Makoto Kyogoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.38,0:00:30.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have the honor of going out with Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.44,0:00:34.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, you're Sonoko's boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.72,0:00:36.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, what's your business?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.92,0:00:41.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It has reached my ears that you hold onto a jewel\Nthat a certain thief intends to take possession of, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.38,0:00:43.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, if you would graciously allow...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.54,0:00:49.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My humble self, Makoto Kyogoku...\NTo have the honor of joining the security detail...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.12,0:00:54.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of man is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.82,0:00:57.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard that he did karate, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.32,0:01:01.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He doesn't just do karate! He was undefeated in 400\Nmatches in a row in tournaments all over the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.74,0:01:05.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He is without equal in a fight —\hthe prince of kicks!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.64,0:01:11.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,U-Undefeated... in 400 matches?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.86,0:01:16.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Please don't place guards inside the room where the jewel will be on display?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.50,0:01:19.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaitō Kid is going to try to steal it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.22,0:01:23.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Advisor Suzuki just called and told me\Nthat people would get in the way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.56,0:01:26.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,of his state-of-the-art security system.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.42,0:01:34.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-One man is... Surrounded by a\Nbunch of men pointing guns at him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.88,0:01:39.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, the bullets are BBs, but with this\Nnumber of people at point-blank range...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.32,0:01:46.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And taking into account that the field of vision of the man in the middle is obstructed by the gas mask,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.54,0:01:49.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you'd think he had no chance of\Navoiding the bullets, wouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.42,0:02:02.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's the world's strongest security system.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.22,0:02:05.84,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But, Tomoko paid a visit to Makoto,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.92,0:02:08.80,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and so did Kid with Sonoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.22,0:02:12.22,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Each offered some kind of bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.34,0:02:17.03,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We won't give in to the hot blazing sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.03,0:02:18.84,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A gallant and dashing deduction show!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.84,0:02:20.46,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Kaitō Kid's surprise strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.46,0:02:22.34,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The battle of the security systems is on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.34,0:02:23.90,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.90,0:02:25.66,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.66,0:02:28.02,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:14.98,Title,,0,0,0,,Kaito Kid VS Makoto Kyogoku\N(Part Two)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.06,0:04:17.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good luck, Makoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:19.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:21.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:24.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,believe in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:28.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. I will protect it until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:31.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You may bet on this fist without fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:34.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Sonoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:52.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I also believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:56.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that you will keep that promise you made.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:04:58.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:02.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:06.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right. I'll be counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.99,0:05:14.50,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Won't you make a bet with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:16.92,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A... bet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.92,0:05:22.21,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If you manage to protect the jewel,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:27.80,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I shall consider that a sign of heaven\Nand accept you as Sonoko's partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.80,0:05:32.18,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}However, should, on the other hand,\Nthat thief manage to beat you,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.18,0:05:35.77,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}you will give up on Sonoko once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.77,0:05:37.27,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Do we have a deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.94,0:05:48.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kid! Kid! Kid! Kid! Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.37,0:06:01.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:06.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?! Letters from Kid arrived here at the museum?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.97,0:06:10.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And addressed to this man again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:13.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, about 100 letters, all at once...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.01,0:06:15.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-One hundred?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.06,0:06:20.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would seem that the writing is invisible again...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.61,0:06:26.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh geez, we can't go through\N100 letters one by one with a lighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:29.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, might you be so good\Nas to prepare a candle and a candle stick?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.70,0:06:33.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we use those to heat the letters,\Nwe can save a lot of time and effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:39.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Somebody bring a candle and a candlestick!{uso}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.59,0:06:45.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:48.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The greatest thief in the whole world never lets his prey escape."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.97,0:06:51.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Nothing is impossible for the moonlight magician."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:56.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The opponent is the world's strongest security system? Challenge accepted!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:07:01.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're all completely pointless!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:08.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Move away, move away! Move a bit further away please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.49,0:07:09.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the hey?{uso}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:11.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't have you coming near it anymore!{uso?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.41,0:07:16.03,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You can't really call that a public display anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:22.37,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But what is it? This huge number of letters...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:27.88,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Is it meant to unsettle Kyogoku{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:29.59,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Or...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.59,0:07:31.88,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Kid! Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.13,0:07:34.26,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The museum is now closing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.26,0:07:39.14,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Visitors are asked to leave the premises in a timely fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:45.40,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Thank you for visiting today.{uso?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:48.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kid! Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:54.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, fall as always, Kaitō Kid!{uso?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.70,0:07:58.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today I'll show you something you won't forget so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.87,0:08:01.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You, that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.87,0:08:05.46,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I have a bad feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:09.92,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}As though we've been had by him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.92,0:08:12.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.68,0:08:15.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You look a bit grim...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.84,0:08:16.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:20.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think of my outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:23.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I chose the most conservative one, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.19,0:08:25.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I think it suits you very well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:28.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You do? That's good...{uso}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:35.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}C-Conservative? It shows way too much cleavage!{uso}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.49,0:08:38.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Makoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.95,0:08:44.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm dressed like this now, so don't you forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:47.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.68,0:08:58.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, only five minutes until\Nthe announced time arrives...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.51,0:09:01.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I would like to ask everyone\Nto leave this exhibition room...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:08.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From now on, until this is over,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:12.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I shall consider anyone who enters this room an enemy,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.11,0:09:14.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and aim to defeat them with all my might.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.91,0:09:19.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, got it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.16,0:09:25.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you!{uso}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.26,0:09:39.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright! Us as well, we won't let anyone pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:41.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.89,0:09:44.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go to the bathroom for a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:46.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.52,0:09:50.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those are the letters from Kid, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:52.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.11,0:09:55.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since there are so many of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.65,0:09:58.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,did the mailman deliver them directly\Nto the back office of the museum?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.11,0:10:04.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No... Miss Sonoko said earlier that\Nshe received them from the mailman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.29,0:10:06.79,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sonoko did?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.41,0:10:09.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was she wearing that dress at the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.33,0:10:12.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good work, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:17.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes... She said that when she went to look\Naround outside after changing into the dress,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.76,0:10:20.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,she happened to meet the mailman,\Nwhom she knew by sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.22,0:10:27.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me see those letters for a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.27,0:10:29.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't intend to take them out of the bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:30.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.73,0:10:35.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}As I thought, it doesn't react to black light!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.49,0:10:40.49,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Which means... Could it be that Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.37,0:10:43.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-Blackout?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.46,0:10:56.92,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm sorry... Makoto{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:08.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kid! Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.19,0:11:13.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-Blackout?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.77,0:11:16.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's something glowing up there...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:18.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Quite a lot of things...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.90,0:11:21.36,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Fluorescent paint?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:29.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? There are some strange things rolling towards us...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.83,0:11:33.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}, get away from them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.67,0:11:41.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nobody panic! It's the usual sleeping gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.88,0:11:44.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you've got your gas mask on, this is nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.69,0:11:54.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.40,0:12:02.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Kid...!{uso}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:11.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:15.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Makoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}! Can I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.64,0:12:28.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Makoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:31.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, what on earth happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.89,0:12:37.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaitō Kid's cut all the power and filled\Nthe whole mansion with sleeping gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.48,0:12:43.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wasn't knocked out because I'd been given\Nthis mask by one of the squad members...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:48.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All the other squad members had their\Ngas masks cut off by Kid's card gun...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:55.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My word...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.58,0:12:59.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was something like fluorescent paint on the gas masks,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.29,0:13:02.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so using the light from those, Kid in the dark...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:05.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In which case, he's still around here somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.88,0:13:08.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think he would've run away already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.93,0:13:13.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And apparently before the power cut\Nthere was a card from Kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:16.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,saying, "I have helped myself to the jewel"...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:20.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That can't be right! The jewel's been around\Nmy neck the whole time, just like so!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.19,0:13:24.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's check that somewhere with better light,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:27.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,whether it's the real jewel or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.58,0:13:35.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't really tell with the moonlight from the window...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:36.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then perhaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.04,0:13:39.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,with a candle...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:40.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:42.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one for revealing invisible ink!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:49.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The real jewel was green wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.43,0:13:54.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Red! It's shining red!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:58.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it! Kid's switched it with a fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.27,0:13:59.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.19,0:14:03.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When? How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.36,0:14:10.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any case, I'll go and hand this fake over to the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.66,0:14:13.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.37,0:14:18.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Makoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you should go and\Nhelp the sleeping squad members!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:23.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:27.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You are not Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:34.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wha... what are you saying? I'm the real one,\Nof course! Although this jewel's a fake...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.35,0:14:36.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, that jewel's the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:39.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C-Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.23,0:14:45.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alexandrite is a dark green under lights,\Nsuch as sunlight or the museum's fluorescent lights,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.61,0:14:50.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that are strong in the blue-green part\Nof the visible light spectrum.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:55.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But under incandescent or candle lights, that are\Nstronger in the red part of the visible light spectrum,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:57.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it shines a vivid red instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.70,0:14:58.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words,{uso}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:15:04.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,those hundreds of meaningless invisible ink letters were sent
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.34,0:15:08.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,in order to ensure that candles would be kept here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:14.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those were letters you had hidden\Nsomewhere in advance in the museum,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.26,0:15:17.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and then, disguised as Sonoko,\Ngave to a squad member, weren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.31,0:15:20.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, if they'd gone through the post office\Nand ended up coming into contact with some heat,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:22.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then the letters wouldn't be invisible any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.90,0:15:30.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As proof of this, there were no barcodes used by the\Npost office for area demarcation on any of the letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.07,0:15:34.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No trace of the invisible ink\Nthat usually shows up under black light!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:41.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So are you saying that Kid stripped off\Nmy clothes and disguised himself as me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.58,0:15:42.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:48.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko took off her clothes and\Nhanded them over to Kid herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.17,0:15:52.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to set things up for the bet she made with Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.34,0:15:53.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A bet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.30,0:16:00.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right! A bet on whether Kyogoku{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} could tell
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:04.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the difference between a Kid disguised\Nas Sonoko and the real Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:14.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn it! He dodged!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:22.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}O-Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:32.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where... Where is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.64,0:16:45.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Green Emperor is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.94,0:16:54.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But for now, why don't curse your\Nown flightless self's incompetence...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.36,0:16:58.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. World's Strongest Security System?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.74,0:17:00.37,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:06.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give me some space.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.22,0:17:20.47,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}T-The pillar... with karate?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.47,0:17:24.43,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He can't be knocking down all the\Npillars to bring down the ceiling?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:29.69,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Okay, I'm scared! I'd better make myself scarce quickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.16,0:17:45.58,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.38,0:17:52.46,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}H-He flew?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.13,0:18:00.10,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}As expected of the World's Strongest...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.10,0:18:03.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now then... I would like to have them back...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.81,0:18:08.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Both the jewel... and Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.86,0:18:14.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course... it wasn't what I was looking for,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:16.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I will be able to return the jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.82,0:18:20.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the young lady's heart\Nis a different matter entirely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.12,0:18:22.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:30.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You say return, but it wasn't even stolen in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.34,0:18:37.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not at the point when I offered the terms of this bet...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:42.80,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}O-Okay! I'll take that bet, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:46.39,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't hurt him, alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.39,0:18:50.52,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Makoto{\rHonorifics - Flashback\be10}-san{\r\be10}'s got... a really big\Ntournament coming up next week...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.81,0:18:52.90,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.19,0:18:56.65,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}K-Kaitō Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.49,0:18:59.20,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.20,0:19:03.37,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It seems as though you won't be able\Nto keep this visit of mine a secret,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.37,0:19:05.74,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}so make up some reasonable lies for your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:09.33,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Especially for that little boy with glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:15.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But unfortunately,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.38,0:19:19.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and even though I've still ended up\Ngiving you a few scrapes and bruises,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:23.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,this bet was won completely and utterly...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.64,0:19:32.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,by that young lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.74,0:21:08.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:12.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He took off all her clothes and left her locked in the toilet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.83,0:21:14.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true, Sonoko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.75,0:21:16.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:18.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's merciless even to the girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.84,0:21:22.59,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Kid told her to say that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.59,0:21:24.30,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Otherwise she'd be accused of being his accomplice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.30,0:21:28.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the moment he put the fluorescent\Npaint on the gas masks must have been...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.76,0:21:30.60,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Good work, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.73,0:21:35.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...then!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.27,0:21:39.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn! That rotten Kid...{uso}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.52,0:21:46.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, young man, you did an\Nexcellent job protecting the jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.53,0:21:50.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't say I did. He got away, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.99,0:21:52.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me...{uso}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.58,0:21:54.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh, don't worry about it.{uso}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.83,0:21:58.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next time, our battle will continue{???}, and then...{uso}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.92,0:22:01.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. Then, without fail...{uso}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.79,0:22:03.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've spoken well.{???uso}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.46,0:22:06.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, you're the world's strongest security system!{???uso}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.43,0:22:12.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's quite the strapping young man!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.81,0:22:13.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.43,0:22:19.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he's a focused, simple, well-mannered, and very strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.19,0:22:23.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he would definitely be fun to tease...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.52,0:22:24.69,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She scares me...{uso}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.86,0:22:29.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry, Makoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}... testing you like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.99,0:22:31.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah... it's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.53,0:22:32.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One more thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.16,0:22:37.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did you realize that it was Kid in disguise?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.58,0:22:41.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was it something like, because the real me is even prettier?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.71,0:22:44.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right? Something like that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.63,0:22:47.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.01,0:22:49.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.93,0:23:01.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unlike me, Kid's ring finger is longer than his index finger?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.52,0:23:03.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You actually noticed that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.52,0:23:10.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes... I've got into the habit of assessing all\Nmy opponent's physical features in a glance...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.07,0:23:12.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was there really nothing else at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.32,0:23:15.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like the real me seems more pure or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.45,0:23:17.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,P-Pure?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.62,0:23:21.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, pure, innocent...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.25,0:23:24.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, forget it!{XXXuso}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.25,0:23:26.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.46,0:23:27.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.71,0:23:33.01,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Well, they say that girls usually have\Nlonger index fingers than ring fingers
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.01,0:23:36.76,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and guys vice versa because of the\Nrelationship between fingers and hormones.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.76,0:23:39.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Although there are plenty of exceptions to that...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.27,0:23:42.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, my ring finger's really long!
